trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartitionCollection" /> class is a read-only collection that contains <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartitionCollection" /> é uma coleção somente leitura que contém objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object to search for in this collection.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> a ser pesquisado nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: Determines if the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object is in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Determina se o objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> especificado está nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> is in this collection, otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se o <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> estiver nesta coleção, caso contrário, <see langword="false" />.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The array of <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> objects that receives the elements of this collection.
trans-unit.target: A matriz de objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> que recebe os elementos desta coleção.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index in <c>applicationPartitions</c> where this method starts copying this collection.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero em <c>applicationPartitions</c> em que esse método inicia a cópia desta coleção.

trans-unit.source: Copies all <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> objects in this collection to the specified array, starting at the specified index of the target array.
trans-unit.target: Copia todos os objetos <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> nesta coleção para a matriz especificada, iniciando no índice especificado na matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: Uma chamada ao serviço do diretório subjacente resultou em um erro.

trans-unit.source: The destination array is not large enough, based on the source collection size and the <paramref name="index" /> specified.
trans-unit.target: A matriz de destino não é grande o suficiente, com base no tamanho da coleção de origem e no <paramref name="index" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="applicationPartitions" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="applicationPartitions" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> specified is out of range of the destination array.
trans-unit.target: O <paramref name="index" /> especificado está fora do intervalo da matriz de destino.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object to search for in this collection.
trans-unit.target: O objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> a ser pesquisado nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: Returns the first occurrence of the specified <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Retorna a primeira ocorrência do objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> especificado nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the first matching item.
trans-unit.target: O índice baseado em zero do primeiro item correspondente.

trans-unit.source: -1 if no member of this collection is identical to <paramref name="applicationPartition" />.
trans-unit.target: -1 se nenhum membro dessa coleção for idêntico a <paramref name="applicationPartition" />.

trans-unit.source: A call to the underlying directory service resulted in an error.
trans-unit.target: Uma chamada ao serviço do diretório subjacente resultou em um erro.

trans-unit.source: <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> is <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="applicationPartition" /> é <see langword="null" />.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object to get.
trans-unit.target: O índice de base zero do objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> a ser obtido.

trans-unit.source: Gets an <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object in this collection.
trans-unit.target: Obtém um objeto <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> nesta coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> object that exists at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: O <see cref="T:System.DirectoryServices.ActiveDirectory.ApplicationPartition" /> objeto que existe no índice especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <paramref name="index" /> specified is out of range of the collection.
trans-unit.target: O <paramref name="index" /> especificado está fora do intervalo da coleção.
